Rating: 4
This is a great, easy recipe. I have made it many times. One suggestion is to remove the skin from chicken, as the marinade penetrates better. It's healthier and the outer layer gets crispy this way. Also, don't drench the chicken in so much marinade that it drips off the chicken - because the extra marinade will just burn and smoke in the oven. Save extra marinade to recoat the chicken when you take it out to flip.

